## ‚ö†Ô∏è Critical Considerations

### 1. Preserve Existing Functionality
- ‚úÖ Keep profile system we just implemented
- ‚úÖ Maintain authentication flow
- ‚úÖ Keep all API integrations
- ‚úÖ Preserve 3D map functionality
- ‚úÖ Keep role-based access control

### 2. Responsive Design
- Mobile sidebar should slide out/in
- Stat cards should stack on mobile
- Tables should scroll horizontally on small screens

### 3. Dark Mode
- Argon includes dark mode support
- Consider implementing toggle in settings
- Update all custom components for dark mode

### 4. Performance
- Lazy load Argon JS/CSS only where needed
- Don't load chart libraries on non-dashboard pages
- Optimize icon fonts (tree-shake unused icons if possible)

